CommonFields.Title: Physical aging of single wall carbon nanotube polymer nanocomposites: effect of functionalization of the nanotube on the enthalpy relaxation
Author: Anny L. Flory
T. Ramanathan
L. Catherine Brinson

Mixing.Description: precipitation of the mixture in methanol and filtration of the precipitate using a polytetrafluoroethylene filter paper with a pore size of 10 μm

data.description: Change in enthalpy versus log aging time
Temperature of the C peak versus enthalpy.
Logarithmic cooling rate as a function of the reciprocal fictive temperature. Values of Δh/R (kK) are given by the slope of the lines.
